  "edgeCases": [
    "Disabled config ([telemetry] enabled=false) is a no-op: no file written, no events recorded.",
    "Default-on (opt-out): absent [telemetry] section still records events (IsEnabled returns true when Enabled==nil).",
    "Non-blocking on I/O error: unwritable telemetry dir / marshal failure warns to stderr and returns nothing; host command exit code and control flow unchanged.",
    "nil config: Record(nil, e) is a no-op (prewrite hook may pass a defaulted/nil cfg).",
    "Lenient Read: a corrupt/garbage line is skipped; valid events on other lines are still returned, no error.",
    "Missing log file: Read returns (nil, nil) with no error.",
    "block need-init vs out-of-step: need-init carries no feature/step; out-of-step carries feature+step; both carry fileType+targetPath.",
    "gate-failure carries no feature (validate is not feature-scoped); attribution is via the co-occurring complete-rejected{reason:gates} by timestamp proximity in the same process.",
    "One gate-failure event is emitted per gate with status Fail (N fails => N events).",
    "step-advanced carries the JUST-COMPLETED step (current), not the next step, to bracket the rework window.",
    "Rework derivation: N complete-rejected for (feature,step) before the step-advanced for that same (feature,step) => rework count N; no workflow state stored.",
    "Schema + timestamp stamped on every event by Record: schema=centinela.telemetry/v1, timestamp RFC3339 UTC (overridable now clock for deterministic tests).",
    "Append-only ordering: multiple Records accumulate in call order; earlier lines never overwritten.",
    "Worktree-safe append: O_APPEND single-line writes are atomic on local FS; two sequential Records both land as complete JSON lines (no flock).",
    "CheckRef is an owned flat copy (claim/role/status/detail) — telemetry does NOT import verify.Check, staying a leaf; cmd-local toCheckRefs maps verify.Check -> CheckRef."
  ],
